title: Mid-size luxury vehicles : sales by model in the United States 2019
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 17 different Models on X-axis for 2 groups 2019, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Model Tesla Model 3 had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 2 groups, and it was for 2019. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Model Acura RLX for 2019.
Among all the Models, 2018 had the highest SOME LABEL 140317.0 in Model Tesla Model 3 and lowest value 1931.0 in Model Acura RLX.
There is a gap of 138386.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2018 in Model Tesla Model 3 and Acura RLX.
